title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: It is beginning to dawn on you that certain habits and practices are keeping you from embracing your full authenticity. These patterns might be your attempts to deceive yourself or conceal your flaws from others. For instance, in the past you may have projected inadequacies onto everyone else rather than face your own fears and shortcomings. When you take an objective inventory of yourself now, you dont necessarily like everything you see. Thankfully, viewing the truth puts you one step closer to living your life with complete integrity. Poet May Sarton wrote, We have to dare to be ourselves. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
